modName: Warm-Natural FXAA Preset for Pure Weather
summary: This FXAA preset is intended to be used with Pure Weather by Laast. It will give your game a warmer, natural sort of look, with almost no FPS loss.
descriptionHtml:
Hi! this is my very first upload on Nexus :) I made this preset using FXAA Post Process Injector tool.

This FXAA preset is intended to be used with Pure Weather by Laast.
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52423/?
It will give your game a warmer, natural sort of look, with almost no FPS loss. Both Pure Weather and this preset work very well on low-end computers.
author: MotherFvcker
